WEBVTT

00:00:01.708 --> 00:00:04.292
I want to tell you
about a student of mine.

00:00:05.167 --> 00:00:08.559
A few weeks ago, she was on vacation

00:00:08.583 --> 00:00:11.768
when at 3am she got a phone call.

00:00:11.792 --> 00:00:13.309
It was her husband telling her

00:00:13.333 --> 00:00:18.893
that the city that she was in
would be quarantined by 10am.

00:00:18.917 --> 00:00:20.726
She was in Wuhan, China.

00:00:20.750 --> 00:00:23.125
The epicenter of the coronavirus outbreak.

00:00:24.708 --> 00:00:28.101
By 8am she was on the road
in a friend's car

00:00:28.125 --> 00:00:30.875
driving 500 miles to Shanghai Airport.